title: UFOs Not NOT Aliens? Avenger’s Campus Orientation 6.7.21

description:
In episode 924, Jack and guest host Jamie Loftus are joined by comedian Yassir Lester to discuss the new covid variants coming, Facebook's ban on Trump, a US intel report on UFOs, the new Avengers campus at Disneyland, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. ‘Pfizer vaccine generates fewer antibodies against Delta variant’
  2. Facebook suspends Trump for 2 years in response to Oversight Board ruling
  3. US intel report on UFOs: No evidence of aliens, but. ...
  4. Report does not confirm, or rule out, extraterrestrial activity in unexplained aerial events
  5. Avengers Campus Review: Disneyland's Newest Addition Is A Marvel Fan's Dream Come True
  6. LISTEN: U-Roy & Santigold - Man Next Door
